{"tid":1677273,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"男子冒警闖沙田麗豪酒店房搜查 內地女失財4.3萬","createTime":"2019-10-27T04:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T05:17:57.000Z","uid":242537,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e92e75a67a6b4623ffa3578837affe64f47e67d0","tid":1677273,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/waiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwaiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png&h=e65c484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EBs-CzWVUAEDhvh?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEBs-CzWVUAEDhvh%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=67561c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EBs-CzVUwAEAXL2?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEBs-CzVUwAEAXL2%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=3997c738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名29歲內地女子凌晨在沙田麗豪酒店，遭一名涉嫌冒警的男子搜查房間後，失去共4.3萬元財物。<br />\n<br />\n現場為大湧橋路34至36號。該名男子早前在酒店向事主聲稱自己為警務人員，要求在房間內檢查財物，事主後發現約3萬元現金及一條價值約1.3萬元的手鐲不見了。<br />\n<br />\n警方凌晨2時41分接報到場，經初步調查後，案件列作冒充警務人員及盜竊，交由沙田警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進，暫時無人被捕，正追緝一名身高約1.7米，案發時身穿深色短袖上衣、淺藍色長褲及戴帽子的男子。"},{"pid":"cb19ae159e73d2ca74148afd3330606d3fe5deaa","tid":1677273,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:06:59.000Z","msg":"支持警察呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1123d36f6fc18475b11d35b8fc3a11539b34e0ed","tid":1677273,"uid":6347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:08:25.000Z","msg":"可能真係警察<br />\n不過無show證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e83ea1015